name: Can Haz Cahfee!
description:
You're trying to get to work, which is approximately a million miles away. To get there on time, you need plenty of coffee!

Coffee gives you energy which increases your speed and if you drink enough, you can harness the extra energy to shoot fireballs! Defeat the enemies that stand in your way and collect coins to earn points.

The farther you make, the more points you get. How high of a score can you get?

Controls: space to jump, left mouse button to shoot fireballs.

Credits: Assets by Kenney. Everything else by Chris Delisa
